==播出方式==
第四台在開播時以無線類比電視形式播出訊號，這也是當時英國唯一的電視播出方式。由於第四台具有公共服務特殊地位，其可在無線電視免費播出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ofcom.org.uk/tv/psb_review/digitalpsb/digitalpsb.pdf |title=Digital PSB, Public Service Broadcasting post Digital Switchover, section 1.1 |publisher=OFCOM |access-date=2006-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091009182737/http://www.ofcom.org.uk/tv/psb_review/digitalpsb/digitalpsb.pdf |archive-date=2009-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.itvplc.com/itv/news/releases/pr2005/2005-06-29/ |title=Ofcom determination of financial terms for Channel 3 licences ITV plc response |publisher=ITV plc |access-date=2007-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061015170803/http://www.itvplc.com/itv/news/releases/pr2005/2005-06-29/ |archive-date=2006-10-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

第四台可在英國以外的眾多地區收看，包括[[愛爾蘭共和國|愛爾蘭]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[比利時|比利時]]和[[瑞士|瑞士]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.upc.ch/en/television/tv-channels/ |title=Channels – Television | upc cablecom |publisher=Upc-cablecom.ch |access-date=2021-07-16 |archive-date=2021-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629043247/https://www.upc.ch/en/television/tv-channels/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第四台在盧森堡廣播管理局（ALIA） 註冊，並通過該機構在歐盟/EEA播出<ref>{{Cite web|last=Cropmark|date=2021-04-15|title=Supervisory activities|url=https://www.alia.lu/en/television/supervisory-activities|access-date=2021-04-17|website=alia.lu|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627141512/https://www.alia.lu/en/television/supervisory-activities|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.alia.lu/assets/upload/files/2021-03-17Liste-des-services-de-television-maj-mars-2021_site-ALIA.pdf |title=Services de télévision sur antenne soumis au contrôle de l'ALIA |language=fr |publisher=ALIA |access-date=2021-06-22 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320130933/https://www.alia.lu/assets/upload/files/2021-03-17Liste-des-services-de-television-maj-mars-2021_site-ALIA.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年開始，第四台通過[[英國三軍廣播服務|英國三軍廣播服務]]（BFBS）向世界各地的英軍及他們的家人播出。

第四台網站允許英國國內用戶在網路上觀看第四台直播。但部分節目（主要是進口節目）並不在網上播出。第四台亦在[[維珍移動|維珍移動]]的[[數碼聲音廣播|數碼聲音廣播]]移動電視上提供服務<ref>{{cite web |title=TVCatchup – Channel 4 |url=http://www.tvcatchup.com/watch.html?c=4#4 |access-date=2014-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108154407/http://www.tvcatchup.com/watch.html?c=4#4 |archive-date=2014-01-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Andrews|first=Robert|title=ITV, C4, Five Also Get Yanked From Zattoo|url=http://paidcontent.org/2010/06/15/419-itv-c4-five-also-get-yanked-from-zattoo/|access-date=2014-01-08|newspaper=paidContent|date=2010-06-15|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108154158/http://paidcontent.org/2010/06/15/419-itv-c4-five-also-get-yanked-from-zattoo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==資金==
在開播初期，第四台的財源來自其它ITV公司。{{link-en|1990年廣播法|Broadcasting Act 1990}}通過之後，第四台的資金來源發生很大變化，不再依賴ITV。現在第四台和大多數商業廣播相同，其財源通過廣告、節目贊助、節目及版權銷售等方式獲得。{{as of|2012|lc=y}}，第四台總收入有9.25億英鎊，其中91%來自廣告<ref>{{cite web |url=http://annualreport.channel4.com/Downloads/Channel4_AR12_financials.pdf |title=Financial report and statements |year=2013 |publisher=Channel 4 |pages=112–114 |access-date=2013-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105030740/http://annualreport.channel4.com/Downloads/Channel4_AR12_financials.pdf |archive-date=2013-11-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 

2007年，由於嚴重的財務困難，第四台尋求政府幫助，並在六年期間內獲得1,400萬英鎊資助。這一資金來自於[[電視授權|電視授權]]費用，而這是電視授權費第一次用於BBC以外的企業<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/jowell-challenges-channel-4-to-justify-16314m-of-public-funding-454035.html |work=The Independent |location=London |title=Jowell challenges Channel 4 to justify £14m of public funding |first=Ian |last=Burrell |date=2007-06-21 |access-date=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2008-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208112623/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/jowell-challenges-channel-4-to-justify-16314m-of-public-funding-454035.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而這一計劃被時任[[數碼文化傳媒及體育大臣|數碼文化傳媒及體育大臣]][[安迪·伯纳姆|安迪·伯纳姆]]廢除<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7750501.stm |work=BBC News |title=Channel 4 switchover cash shelved |date=2008-11-26 |access-date=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2021-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629044214/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7750501.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。廣播監管機構[[Ofcom|Ofcom]]在2009年公佈了一份報告，建議第四台考慮通過「夥伴關係、合資或合併」解決資金問題<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stakeholders.ofcom.org.uk/consultations/psb2_phase2/statement/ |title=Ofcom's second Public Service Broadcasting Review – Phase Two: preparing for the digital future |website=Ofcom |date=2016-09-22 |access-date=2021-07-16 |archive-date=2016-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823115935/http://stakeholders.ofcom.org.uk/consultations/psb2_phase2/statement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==節目==
第四台是一家「出版廣播商（publisher-broadcaster）」，其節目均購買自外部的獨立製作公司。第四台也是英國第一家將節目製作完全外包的電視台，而這一特徵亦被規定在其播出執照內<ref name="schools"/><ref name="licence"/>。這也使得製作公司不必再依賴ITV作為其節目唯一的播出渠道。另一方面，雖然第四台是英國第一個將所有節目外包的英國電視台，但其也是英國最後一家將播出業務外包的無線電視台<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/nov/14/channel4.television1 |work=The Guardian |location=London |title=Channel 4 outsources to Red Bee |first=Caitlin |last=Fitzsimmons |date=2007-11-14 |access-date=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309034109/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/nov/14/channel4.television1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

