==區域版本==
和在不同地區播出不同內容的BBC及ITV不同，第四台自開播以來就在英國全國播出同樣節目內容。但在1980年代至1990年代初期，第四台部分學校節目按地區播出不同內容。且不同地區亦會播出不同廣告<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.4sales.com/our-offering/regional-information |title=Regional Information |website=4Sales |access-date=2021-07-16 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128124750/https://www.4sales.com/our-offering/regional-information |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4sales.com/data/macro_map |title=Channel 4's 'Macro Regions' for advertising, including a map |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220084700/http://www.channel4sales.com/data/macro_map |archive-date=2008-12-20 |access-date=2021-07-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於[[獨立電視公司|獨立電視公司]]要求監管當局放寬對其地區新聞的數量要求，有構想由第四台承擔部分地區新聞製作的。[[Ofcom|Ofcom]]、ITV和第四台正在對此事進行談判<ref name="c4moveregional">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/jul/03/channel4.ofcom |title=Channel 4 ponders move into regional news as ITV retreats |work=The Guardian |author=Leigh Holmwood |date=2008-03-07 |access-date=2008-09-30 |location=London |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308224347/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/jul/03/channel4.ofcom |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==第四台HD==
2006年，第四台進行了為期六個月的[[高畫質電視|高畫質電視]]試驗，通過{{link-en|水晶宮發射站|Crystal Palace transmitting station}}向倫敦和部分[[倫敦周圍各郡|倫敦周圍各郡]]發射訊號<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ofcom.org.uk/consult/condocs/ddr/ddr_annexed.pdf |title=Digital Dividend Review Annexes |website=Ofcom |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070615192453/http://www.ofcom.org.uk/consult/condocs/ddr/ddr_annexed.pdf |archivedate=2007-06-15 |access-date=2021-07-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2007年12月10日，第四台開始在天空數位衛星電視上播出高畫質聯播頻道，這也是英國第一個由無線電視台提供的完全高畫質電視頻道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dtg.org.uk/dtg/press_releases/dtg_nmm_20100318.pdf|title=BBC HD strategy comes into focus as Five opts for BSkyB, not Freeview|publisher=New Media Markets|date=2010-03-18|access-date=2010-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722130613/http://www.dtg.org.uk/dtg/press_releases/dtg_nmm_20100318.pdf|archive-date=2011-07-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2009年7月31日，維珍媒體上開始播出第四台HD頻道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a168390/c4-hd-coming-to-virgin-media-tomorrow.html|title=C4 HD coming to Virgin Media tomorrow|website=Digital Spy|date=2009-07-30|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015213407/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a168390/c4-hd-coming-to-virgin-media-tomorrow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年3月25日，第四台HD開始在[[Freeview|Freeview]]上播出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a210797/c4-hd-begins-freeview-test-transmissions.html|title=C4 HD begins Freeview test transmissions|website=Digital Spy|date=2010-03-26|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015213407/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a210797/c4-hd-begins-freeview-test-transmissions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reghardware.com/2010/03/30/freeview_hd_launches_gets_channel_4/|title=Freeview HD launches, gets Channel 4|publisher=Register Hardware|date=2010-03-30|access-date=2013-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116072206/http://www.reghardware.com/2010/03/30/freeview_hd_launches_gets_channel_4/|archive-date=2013-01-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2011年4月19日，第四台HD開始在{{link-en|Freesat|Freesat}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joinfreesat.co.uk/channel-4-hd-finally-arrives-on-freesat/|title=Channel 4 HD Finally Arrives on Freesat|publisher=Join Freesat|date=2011-04-19|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116041211/http://www.joinfreesat.co.uk/channel-4-hd-finally-arrives-on-freesat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年12月2日開始，第四台HD開始在威爾斯播出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stakeholders.ofcom.org.uk/binaries/spectrum/spectrum-policy-area/projects/dtv/Amendment_to_Determination.pdf|title=Amendment to Determination|date=2012-09-21|website=Ofcom|access-date=2012-10-02|archive-date=2013-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430143005/http://stakeholders.ofcom.org.uk/binaries/spectrum/spectrum-policy-area/projects/dtv/Amendment_to_Determination.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

